  "body": "<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1598757788754-GHOUB6JX1BD7BLLWL131/10a-photo6-600x600.jpg\"/>\n\n\n</figure>\n\n\n<p>Happy Friday everyone! I've got a week's worth of photo prompts up on the<a href=\"http://www.studiocalico.com/blog/2014/6/13/a-week-of-photo-prompts--3?aff=6cc2c70f\"> Studio Calico blog</a>. Hope they inspire you to document some moments in a different way. For this shot, I stacked some of Jack's favorite day time books. He seems really into them. He likes turning the pages and pointing to stuff, and has just started lifting the flaps in the last two. Either styled or unstyled, a group of objects together can be a great reminder of a specific time period. </p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1598757809111-5DTQZNDJ0S5TDYRIS5NY/10b-collection-600x398.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<figcaption>\n<ul><li><p><a href=\"http://www.amazon.com/gp/product/0679882812/ref=as_li_tl?ie=UTF8&amp;camp=1789&amp;creative=390957&amp;creativeASIN=0679882812&amp;linkCode=as2&amp;tag=wwwamytangeri-20\">Dr. Seuss's ABC</a></p></li><li><p><a href=\"http://www.amazon.com/gp/product/1452107556/ref=as_li_tl?ie=UTF8&amp;camp=1789&amp;creative=390957&amp;creativeASIN=1452107556&amp;linkCode=as2&amp;tag=wwwamytangeri-20\">Bus Stops</a></p></li><li><p><a href=\"http://www.amazon.com/gp/product/0983812195/ref=as_li_tl?ie=UTF8&amp;camp=1789&amp;creative=390957&amp;creativeASIN=0983812195&amp;linkCode=as2&amp;tag=wwwamytangeri-20\">123 Brooklyn</a></p></li><li><p><a href=\"http://www.amazon.com/gp/product/0545459036/ref=as_li_tl?ie=UTF8&amp;camp=1789&amp;creative=390957&amp;creativeASIN=0545459036&amp;linkCode=as2&amp;tag=wwwamytangeri-20\">Who's Hiding?</a></p></li><li><p><a href=\"http://www.amazon.com/gp/product/0689835604/ref=as_li_tl?ie=UTF8&amp;camp=1789&amp;creative=390957&amp;creativeASIN=0689835604&amp;linkCode=as2&amp;tag=wwwamytangeri-20\">Where's Baby's Belly Button?</a></p></li></ul><p>Hope <a href=\"http://www.studiocalico.com/blog/2014/6/13/a-week-of-photo-prompts--3?aff=6cc2c70f\">the prompts</a> inspire you to take some photos! Looking forward to seeing what you capture this week. Feel free to link up in the comments below. I will be playing along with my iPhone on Instagram <a href=\"http://instagram.com/amytangerine#\">@amytangerine</a> - with the hashtag #SCphotoprompts.</p>\n</figcaption>\n</figure>"
